QuestData.Title: Down the Goren Hole
QuestData.Description: Dwarves are dumb. Don't they know that if you dig a deep hole you are going to have goren attack?$b$BIf you are going to go into that iron fort you better kill a bunch of goren otherwise they are going to chew the walls enough to cause a cave-in.$b$bI would do it myself but I'm still stuffed from all that fruit the botani made me eat.
